{"tid":895751,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"到底當初點發明到相機同攝錄機?","createTime":"2018-11-09T12:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T14:49:11.000Z","uid":87072,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e787a493b240c2dfda8732d0457fddcf2754b8","tid":895751,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:35:18.000Z","msg":"幾千萬年來，人類都只能用文字同圖畫記錄所見既事物，過左去既野就係過左去，無可能再重現眼前，但相機同攝錄機既誕生，完全改變左人類既歷史，將過去同現在既距離變得好似咫尺之間，由幻想到構想到嘗試再到最後真係實現，成個過程實在太不可思議，太佩服果班發明家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98333781cb81c9f7227cf065c1d4383d1792d9b8","tid":895751,"uid":194474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:49:11.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n影相真係一個breakthrough<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFFtzi3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFFtzi3.png&h=57179208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前見到世界上第一張相真係覺得好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}